Summary: water landing of unknown object still there
trends: There have been 4 other sightings in Forest Lake
There was one other sighting in Forest Lake on or around July 27th 2009
divs: Sighting Detailssometime on or shortly before July 27,2009 A report was made by an eyewitness of an object which fell out of the sky and caused a wave of 30 ft when it hit a lake, near forest lake mn. Object is still there on the bottom. Incident caused a dive team from lower st croix valley fire dept to be activated to locate object. Water was very murky and team was not able to locate object or identify object. Washington county, minnesota , sheriff was involved in incident. I was not a witness but am aware of the dive team activation.
